HR NO. 379 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Louisiana Department of Education 2026
High School Student of the Year Melissa An Le; does hereby recognize her for building a
strong foundation for the future success of the state; and does hereby encourage her to
continue her excellent work and always strive for greatness.
